IN RE the DETENTION OF: B.M. No. 96826-8 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, June 6, 2019

ORDER

¶1 This case came before the Court on its June 6, 2019, En Banc Conference to consider the petition for review. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶3 ORDERED:

¶4 That the petition for review is denied.

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J.

CHIEF JUSTICE
